<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION" />
```
1. Add the following line to your `Info.plist` file in the iOS project:
```xml
<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
<string>Your reason for using location when the app is in use</string>
